org.apache.ignite.internal.pagemem.wal.record

Class LazyDataEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.internal.pagemem.wal.record.DataEntry
      • org.apache.ignite.internal.pagemem.wal.record.LazyDataEntry

  • public class LazyDataEntry
extends DataEntry
    Represents Data Entry (key(), value) pair update operation.
    This Data entry was not converted to key, value pair during record deserialization.
